{"route":{"route":"/posts/854ed6ec/","outputPath":"posts/854ed6ec/index.html","kind":"post","title":"c语言数组输出的另一种方法","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"854ed6ec"}},"post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/c语言数组输出的另一种方法.md","route":"/posts/854ed6ec/","abbrlink":"854ed6ec","title":"c语言数组输出的另一种方法","date":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","updated":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","tags":["C"],"categories":["Program"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:[一个有趣的C语言程序](http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173)\n\n```c\n#include <stdio.h>\n \nint main()\n{\n    int a = 1;\n    int x[5]={1,2,3,4,5};\n    printf(\"%d\",a[x]);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\n```shell\noutput: 2\n```","excerptHtml":"<p>今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:<a href=\"http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173\">一个有趣的C语言程序</a></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> a = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> x[<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>]={<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>};</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,a[x]);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">output: 2</span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:[一个有趣的C语言程序](http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173)\n\n```c\n#include <stdio.h>\n \nint main()\n{\n    int a = 1;\n    int x[5]={1,2,3,4,5};\n    printf(\"%d\",a[x]);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\n```shell\noutput: 2\n```\n\n\nint x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&x[0].\na[x]的等效写法是\\*(a+&x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0].\n所以可以进一步写成\\*(a+&x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成\\*(&x[0]+1),也就是x[1].\n所以就是x[1]对应的值：2\n\n由此我又想到了二位数组\n\n```c\n#include <stdio.h>\n \nint main()\n{\n    int a = 1;\n    int x[2][2]={{1,2},{3,4}};\n    printf(\"%d\",a[a[x]]);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\n```shell\noutput: 4\n```\n\n感觉好神奇,而且在之前不知道在哪看到__c语言的数组其实就是指针的合集__,而且最近要用链表,更觉得链表和数组差不多.","bodyHtml":"<p>今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:<a href=\"http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173\">一个有趣的C语言程序</a></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> a = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> x[<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>]={<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>};</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,a[x]);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">output: 2</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>int x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&amp;x[0].<br>\na[x]的等效写法是*(a+&amp;x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0].<br>\n所以可以进一步写成*(a+&amp;x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成*(&amp;x[0]+1),也就是x[1].<br>\n所以就是x[1]对应的值：2</p>\n<p>由此我又想到了二位数组</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> a = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span> x[<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>][<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]={{<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>},{<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>,<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>}};</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,a[a[x]]);</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">output: 4</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>感觉好神奇,而且在之前不知道在哪看到__c语言的数组其实就是指针的合集__,而且最近要用链表,更觉得链表和数组差不多.</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"\n今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:[一个有趣的C语言程序](http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173)\n\n```c\n#include <stdio.h>\n \nint main()\n{\n    int a = 1;\n    int x[5]={1,2,3,4,5};\n    printf(\"%d\",a[x]);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\n```shell\noutput: 2\n```\n\n<!--more-->\nint x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&x[0].\na[x]的等效写法是\\*(a+&x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0].\n所以可以进一步写成\\*(a+&x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成\\*(&x[0]+1),也就是x[1].\n所以就是x[1]对应的值：2\n\n由此我又想到了二位数组\n\n```c\n#include <stdio.h>\n \nint main()\n{\n    int a = 1;\n    int x[2][2]={{1,2},{3,4}};\n    printf(\"%d\",a[a[x]]);\n    return 0;\n}\n```\n\n```shell\noutput: 4\n```\n\n感觉好神奇,而且在之前不知道在哪看到__c语言的数组其实就是指针的合集__,而且最近要用链表,更觉得链表和数组差不多.\n","plainText":"今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:一个有趣的C语言程序 int x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&x[0]. a[x]的等效写法是\\ (a+&x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0]. 所以可以进一步写成\\ (a+&x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成\\ (&x[0]+1),也就是x[1]. 所以就是x[1]对应的值：2 由此我又想到了二位数组 感觉好神奇,而且在之前不知道在哪看到 c语言的数组其实就是指针的合集 ,而且最近要用链表,更觉得链表和数组差不多.","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"854ed6ec","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}